类 DeferredLog

    public class DeferredLog
extends Object
implements org.apache.commons.logging.Log
    Deferred Log that can be used to store messages that shouldn't be written until the logging system is fully initialized.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.3.0
    作者:
    Phillip Webb
